Developer Terms of Use
des:
Forget those old, boring, buzz and jingle alarms! Wake up to the warm and soothing sounds of cats meowing and purring their brains out! Especially entertaining for your four-footed feline house guests. Cat Meow Alarm features 2 free meow alarms: "Morning Meow," and "Kuddly Kitten," plus a special get-out-of-bed snooze meow: "Tom Cat Growl."

Get Cat Meow Gold to unlock seven MORE Cat Meow alarms including: "Tribblin'," "Lil' Kitten," "Cattin' Around," "Loneliest Kitty," "Kitten Chirps," "Twitter N' Purr," and the very soothing, "Longest Purr."

All meows are made from 100% natural, organic, real-life cats, not from synthesizers, AI algorithms, or GMO felines. No felines were harmed in the creation of this alarm.

FEEDBACK AND SUPPORT: If you enjoyed Cat Meow Alarm, please leave us a review telling us what you love, and what alarms you want to hear next!
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
